        "username": "degremoa"
      },
      "date": "2023-04-17 09:00:53.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> I was going to do another patch after this to try and remove the need for the build/ dir entirely.\n\nA follow up patch that drop the symlinks is fine, they are mostly their for compat I think.\nThe tricky part is the Makefile/Rules.in which is used in ./configure ...",
